Source: poly-c60-profile-media-player
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Maintainer: OpenPolycom <apt@openpolycom.cc>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: poly-c60-profile-media-player
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, poly-app-kodi, poly-kodi-skin-c60portrait
Description: C60 device profile: Kodi media player (portrait)
 Metapackage selecting the media-player role for the Polycom Trio C60:
 Kodi fullscreen on GBM/KMS with the portrait skin and the board's ALSA
 routing. The config blob's PROFILE=media-player selects the kodi engine
 in the kiosk weston stack (KIOSK_ENGINE=kodi).
